It gives me a good understanding, a good overview, about

78
00:05:25,033 --> 00:05:29,933
the major or minor components of the content.

79
00:05:29,933 --> 00:05:31,733
So I see that here...

80
00:05:31,733 --> 00:05:35,633
>>Screen reader: Welcome 2.Featured Stories Slideshow 2.Accessible University 1.

81
00:05:35,633 --> 00:05:41,899
>>Hadi: Accessible University itself is a Heading 1 and under that we have...

82
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:45,266
>>Screen reader: Feature Stories.

83
